// =============================================================================
// REVIEW FLAGS for team-lead / Reine
// =============================================================================
// 1. xpReward: role spec defaults A1 to 50 XP; current Module 4 record has 100.
//    Recommend keeping 100 for parity with Modules 1-3 unless Reine wants a global A1=50 reset.
// 2. Mi Sangre foundation factual claim is marked // REVIEW: verify in the passage.
